{
  "stem": "23428.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But anyway, after having been in the hospital bed there, with-- a-- in a-- in a-- in a hospital compound with other people who couldn't walk anymore-- a column of Red Army soldiers suddenly was-- came in to the camp, the main--",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--street of Auschwitz I.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The main-- it was 28th of January, 1946-- well, '45.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'45, 28th of January.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So needless to say, those of us who could walk ran out and embraced the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Welcome.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the soldiers, strangely enough, were mostly Mongols, tiny Mongols, with sub-machine guns.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then OK, nothing really then happened, except that the Red Army moved an army hospital into the compound.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were put in the care of a Red Army captain, a female captain that took excellent care of us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fed us.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of people died during that period because, obviously, they were not accustomed to eating, and they overfed them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But and there were also other things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I remember during that time, I-- I took care of several days of people had gone insane.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a-- was a whole ward of people who had gone insane.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and I remember spending my days sort of stroking their heads, which was the only way to make them at all comfortable.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And ?] [? amen. ?] And I-- I-- I was also in charge of heating the compound.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I must've carried coal to 20 or 25 coal stoves every morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember polishing other people's shoes, and so I made myself useful.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
